      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in pristine condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects a commitment to excellence, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously maintained interior cabin. Mechanically, the vehicle operates with the precision of a new machine, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards. This is an exceptional opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly unrivaled example of its kind.",
