    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS timing. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a reinforced rear subframe and documented rod bearing service to ensure long-term structural and internal integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise shift gates, delivering power to the rear wheels via a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec with zero bushing play, providing the telepathic handling these chassis are known for. Immaculate Carbon Black paint meets a pristine Nappa leather interior, making this a definitive collector-tier specimen.",
